
                                              GRADE IMPROVEMENT ANALYSIS REPORT 
                                                   JOE WASONGA OCHIENG'   
                                                   28 Jun 2026, 14:08:28 

The Dataset: "The Grade Improvement Analysis Report" : : A 1980 study by L. Spector and M. Mazzeo published in the Journal of 
Economic Education. It analyzes whether a new method of teaching economics—the Personalized System of Instruction 
(PSI)—significantly improves student performance. 
                
                                          * 1. Import and Label Data
---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
. import excel "Table 15.7 Logit.xlsx", sheet("Sheet1") firstrow clear
(5 vars, 32 obs)

. label variable gpa "Entering Grade Point Average (GPA)"

. label variable tuce "Economics Pre-Test Score (TUCE)"

. label variable psi "Personalized System of Instruction (PSI)"

. label variable y "Grade Improvement (Y)"

. label define binary_lbl 0 "No Improvement / Control" 1 "Improved / Treated"

. label values psi binary_lbl

. label values y binary_lbl


